Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:44.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}於是牽住了夥伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:50.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}這樣的話將永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年無憂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:04:02.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論如何都想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:08.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夥伴們曾牽在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:15.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已變得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:19.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一個個漸漸離去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:26.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向著那甦醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:35.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}邁開腳步毅然前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:44.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}彷彿節日的喧囂過後
