Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我和鈴不知道的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成為領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次建立Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候做過的那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代替他完成一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許就能接近那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候恭介建立Little Busters時的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介先是帶著鈴來到了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後先成為朋友的是真人還是謙吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙被通緝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是個很壞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「讓那個傢伙改邪歸正  並拯救了這座城市的人就是我」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前是個什麼樣的城市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人恐怖統治下的貧民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連通緝令都發出來了  貼在電線杆上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後恭介打敗了真人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就和壞小子真人締結了友情的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個夥伴是真人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鈴兩人建立了Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能成為我們的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  告訴我理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你比謙吾要弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概會從現在開始去證明自己是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想受傷的話就不要接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始證明自己是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人到底在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  井之原？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本來不及插手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去告訴老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被井之原打了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被真人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙突然就打了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴裡還喊著什麼我更強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙開始一個接一個的攻擊大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者五人  全都是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是搭話就被單方面毆打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下就被打倒反過來說也算幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好只受了點輕傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙變成壞蛋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能  一定有什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們見到井之原也別蠻幹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上逃走  到教師辦公室報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像變回了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖的貧民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想辦法制止失控的真人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動腦筋好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換成恭介會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  陷阱怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給真人設個局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介也這麼做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有幫忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科學部  拳擊部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一說要制止真人  大家都願意提供材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去貼這些就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  你是不是有些興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去貼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（最強的人到這裡來）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那笨蛋看見這個手套一定會忍不住揍上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介一直計劃和享受著這樣愉快而脫線的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都把它當成人生意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴的眼中重現了昔日的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把這些全打爛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們會全部給我消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他中陷阱了  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼  把電筒關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西  拿不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是特別的強力膠  科學部發明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打的什麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想制止失控的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失控？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是這樣認為的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的人是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下成大事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得制定好新的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  身後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到作戰計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓鈴幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  為了理樹我什麼都幹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人  我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸地東跑西竄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我堂堂正正幹一場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按捺住心中的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人現在全身負著重荷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧妙地引誘他  消磨他的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不投降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你閉嘴  不會讓你再逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會逃走的  因為已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的機關  這就完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  已經沒後手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  有用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了  真人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太讓我驚訝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒想過你們能做到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你教鈴去玩投接球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她回復得足以過來食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鈴兩人建立了Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能成為我們的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  告訴我理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你比謙吾要弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是最強的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters可不是那麼容易就能建立的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒有恭介那麼堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還需要克服很多困難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概會從現在開始去證明自己是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想受傷的話就不要接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到從前？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到從前可沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時起  我就和他人不太相同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世人稱之為笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交不到朋友  不合群的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙口渴的時候居然還喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又開始跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是笨蛋吧  井之原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天生的所以才可笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要不被嘲笑  只有變強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天起  我開始瘋狂地鍛鍊身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於  我變得比任何人都強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也沒有人敢嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原來了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我依舊沒有屬於自己的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想問你是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有瘋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你生活中的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在吵什麼架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  井之原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的我才是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把這些全打爛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們會全部給我消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼  把電筒關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我向我發起了挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他的傢伙不同  他很有骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起其他人  這個我最像我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於出現了  擊敗我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是井之原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是新的挑戰者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這弱不禁風的小身板可沒法跟我鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的戰鬥還是頭一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我製作的機關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的機關  這就完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  已經沒後手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了  看來只能做好被揍幾拳的覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被揍好幾百拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要一隻手就能把你揍個落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你還沒倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你解脫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是為了什麼而在獨自努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變強之後  成為最強之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為就沒人再敢嘲笑我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但回過頭來發現自己還是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我絕不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒下之後就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變回一個單純的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在和你戰鬥過之後感到十分開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊舉著郵筒一邊戰鬥的笨蛋可是世間少有的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就繼續笨蛋下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話今後我還會陪你繼續玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為實在太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原  你的名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:21:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是棗恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人  從今天起我們倆就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後會有很多開心的事情等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在就先休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了  我想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的  真人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不強也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎樣的真人都還是真人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最重要的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後會有開心的事情等著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  所以現在就先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼  我都陪伴著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至最後那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到擊敗無敵之男的時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  摯友之淚
